==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀρχισυνάγωγος / archisunagōgos / ar-khee-soon-ag'-o-gos

===Etymology===
*From [[ἀρχή]] {{GG|746}} and [[συναγωγή]] {{GG|4864}}; 

===Noun===
